Die Pein.

81
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:37,120
Und wirst Betty Winter.

82
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:43,040
[Juliana] <i>I search for you Ech gesicht</i>
<i>Iech am Labyrinth Labirenette</i>

83
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:49,080
<i>Seni ariyorum jeg leter etter deg Zure</i>
<i>bila nabil labirintoan!</i>

84
